title: RECAP: Tech picks up shutout win over CBU - Texas Tech Red Raiders - TexasTech.com
content: RECAP: Tech picks up shutout win over CBU - Texas Tech Red Raiders  TexasTech.com
description: CATHEDRAL CITY, Calif. – Sophomore infielder Arriana Villa recorded three RBI on three hits as the Red Raiders opened the Mary Nutter Collegiate Classic with a 5-0 win over California Baptist Thursday evening. Texas Tech (4-7) snapped a seven-game losing skid with the win, as Kendall Fritz and Maddie Kuehl combined for the shutout.
